              <br>
                III: Be one of the first 5 players to win a given Nemelex' choice combo (+75 tournament points).
              </p>
            </div>

	    <hr>

            <div>
	      <img src="images/banner_okawaru1.png"
                   alt="The Conqueror"
                   title="The Conqueror"
                   width="170" height="58"
                   >
              <p>
                Okawaru is all about winning, all the time, and thus
