              <br>
                I: Reach experience level 13.
              <br>
                II: Win a game.
              <br>
                III: Win a game in under 50000 turns.
              </p>
            </div>

	    <hr>

            <div>
	      <img src="images/banner_qazlal1.png"
                   alt="The Prophet"
                   title="The Prophet"
                   width="170" height="58"
                   >
              <p>
                Qazlal demands fervent worship! Accordingly, Qazlal will only
